# Codebase Analysis — Your Study Companion Mobile (Orbit)

## Project Overview

**Name:** Orbit — Your Study Companion (Mobile)  
**Platform:** React Native (Expo ~54) + Expo Router v6  
**Backend:** Shared with the web app — Express REST API + Supabase (Auth, Storage, Edge Functions)  
**Language:** TypeScript  
**Styling:** StyleSheet-based (dark, #0a0a0a background, `#f27d26` orange primary)  
**App ID:** `com.elzarai.studycompanion`

---

## Architecture at a Glance

```
app/
  _layout.tsx          ← Root layout: AuthProvider + SafeAreaProvider + auth guard
  auth/
    _layout.tsx        ← Stack for auth screens
    login.tsx          ← Renders LoginScreen
  (tabs)/
    _layout.tsx        ← Custom floating pill TabBar (9 tabs)
    index.tsx          ← Dashboard
    ai.tsx             ← Orbit AI
    planner.tsx        ← Study Planner
    gpa.tsx            ← GPA Tracker
    research.tsx       ← Research
    chat.tsx           ← Global Chat
    news.tsx           ← Campus News
    courses.tsx        ← PDF Library
    leaderboard.tsx    ← Leaderboard
src/
  contexts/
    AuthContext.tsx    ← Supabase session + signOut
  lib/
    supabase.ts        ← Supabase client + callEdgeFunction()
    theme.ts           ← colors, spacing, radius, typography, shadow tokens
  types.ts             ← Shared TS interfaces
  services/            ← One file per feature, all call api.ts or callEdgeFunction
  screens/             ← One screen per tab (contains all logic + styles)
  components/
    UI.tsx             ← Skeleton, CardSkeleton, Badge, EmptyState, ListRow, SectionHeader
    Skeleton.tsx       ← (separate skeleton component)
    AI/
      LibraryPanel.tsx ← Modal: pick PDFs → extract via parse-pdf Edge Fn
      StudyToolsPanel.tsx ← Modal: flashcards, quiz, notes, summary via generate-study-tools
```

---

## Design System (`src/lib/theme.ts`)

| Token | Key Values |
|---|---|
| `colors.primary` | `#f27d26` (orange) |
| `colors.background` | `#0a0a0a` |
| `colors.card` | `#141414` |
| `colors.border` | `#222222` |
| `colors.muted` | `#666666` |
| `colors.green` | `#10b981` |
| `colors.red` | `#ef4444` |
| `colors.blue` | `#3b82f6` |
| `spacing` | xs:4, sm:8, md:16, lg:24, xl:32, xxl:48 |
| `radius` | sm:8 → full:9999 |
| `typography` | xs:11 → 4xl:36 |

---

## Navigation & Auth

- **Expo Router file-based routing** — no manual `NavigationContainer`.
- `app/_layout.tsx` wraps everything in `SafeAreaProvider` + `AuthProvider`.
- `RootLayoutNav` uses a `useEffect` on `session` + `segments` to guard routes:
  - No session → `router.replace('/auth/login')`
  - Session + in auth → `router.replace('/(tabs)')`
- Tab layout uses a **custom `FloatingTabBar`** — a dark pill with SVG icons and active-circle highlight. 9 tabs total.

---

## Auth (`src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx`)

- `useRef` guard prevents double `getSession()` calls on StrictMode re-renders.
- Exposes `{ session, user, loading, signOut }`.
- Uses `AsyncStorage` for Supabase session persistence on device.

---

## API Layer (`src/services/api.ts`)

- **Axios** instance with `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` base.
- Request interceptor attaches Supabase `access_token` as Bearer header.
- **Supabase Edge Functions** called directly via `callEdgeFunction()` in `src/lib/supabase.ts` (used for AI, leaderboard, research, parse-pdf, generate-study-tools).

---

## Screens

### Dashboard (`DashboardScreen.tsx`)
- Loads `getFullDashboardStats()`, `getTasks()`, `getActivity()` in `Promise.allSettled`.
- Shows: XP bar, 4 stat cards (GPA, AI sessions, study mins, research), bar chart activity, study plans list, quick actions.
- **Bug:** `insets` from `useSafeAreaInsets()` is used in JSX but not declared in the component (will crash).
- **Bug:** `signOut` and `router` are used in JSX but not imported/declared.

### AI Screen (`AIScreen.tsx`) — most complex
- 3 modes: **Chat**, **Teach**, **Test**.
- PDF context loaded via `LibraryPanel` → `callEdgeFunction('parse-pdf')`.
- AI calls go to `callEdgeFunction('ai-chat')` with SSE streaming.
- Teach mode: chunks PDF pages (5 at a time), auto-advances.
- Model picker modal: Gemini Flash, Gemini Pro, GPT-4o (via OpenRouter).
- Context chips (active docs) shown above input bar.
- Study Tools button opens `StudyToolsPanel`.
- **Bug (minor):** `cleanText` regex uses escaped braces `\\{\\{` — may not strip template markers correctly in production (works fine as string literal but is double-escaped).

### Planner (`PlannerScreen.tsx`)
- CRUD study plans: name, subjects (comma-separated), total hours.
- Shows stats row (total plans, total hours, avg progress), progress bars, subject tags.
- Add via slide-up modal with `pageSheet` presentation.
- `normalizeSubjects` in service handles string or object arrays from backend.

### GPA (`GPAScreen.tsx`)
- Track GPA per semester (0–5 scale, Nigerian university classification).
- `LineChart` from `react-native-chart-kit` for trajectory.
- Colour-coded GPA: green ≥ 3.5, orange ≥ 2.4, red otherwise.
- **Bug:** `chartData` and `Dimensions` are referenced in JSX but never declared in the file. Will crash on render with records.

### Research (`ResearchScreen.tsx`)
- Search via `callEdgeFunction('research-search')` (Serper + AI summary).
- 2 modes: Academic / Projects.
- Tap a result → AI description generated inline via `callEdgeFunction('ai-chat')` with SSE streaming.
- Citation generator: APA, MLA, CHI formats in a bottom sheet modal.
- **Bug:** `import * as Clipboard from 'expo-clipboard'` is **duplicated** on lines 6 and 7 — TypeScript will throw.
- **Bug:** `useSafeAreaInsets` is used (`insets.top`) but not imported.
- `expo-clipboard` is **not** in `package.json` dependencies.

### Leaderboard (`LeaderboardScreen.tsx`)
- Calls `callEdgeFunction('get-leaderboard')`.
- Podium view for top 3, full scrollable table below.
- "My rank" highlight card when user is outside top 3.
- Avatars via DiceBear API (`/7.x/initials/svg`).
- **Bug:** `MEDAL` constant (emoji array) is referenced in JSX but never declared.

### Courses (`CoursesScreen.tsx`)
- Lists PDFs from `api.get('/api/pdfs')`.
- No upload from mobile (intentionally — user uploads from web).
- Long-press or tap "Remove" button to delete PDF.

### Chat (`ChatScreen.tsx`)
- Global study hub channel, basic send/receive.
- No real-time subscription yet ("Realtime coming soon" in header).
- `receiver_id` optional in `sendChatMessage`.

### News (`NewsScreen.tsx`)
- Campus news from `api.get('/api/news')`.
- Category filter tabs (All, Academic, Events, Research, General).
- Skeleton cards on load.
- Fallback Unsplash image for missing thumbnails.

### Login (`LoginScreen.tsx`)
- Sign in / Create Account toggle.
- **Bug:** `SafeAreaView` imported from both `react-native` (line 5) and `react-native-safe-area-context` (line 7) — the second one shadows the first but causes a duplicate import warning.

---

## Components

### `LibraryPanel.tsx`
- Slide-up modal: lists user PDFs, multi-select, then calls `callEdgeFunction('parse-pdf')` for each.
- Combines text + pages from all selected docs and passes up via `onPdfsExtracted`.
- **Bug:** References `pdf.filePath` then `pdf.file_path` — the `Document` type only defines `uploadedAt`, `size`, `category`, `totalPages`, `scannedPages`. Neither `filePath` nor `file_path` are on the type.

### `StudyToolsPanel.tsx`
- Generates flashcards, quiz, notes, summary from PDF context.
- Calls `callEdgeFunction('generate-study-tools')`.
- **Bug:** Variable is named `pdfContext` in props but referenced as `pdfContent` in `handleGenerate` call. Will always throw a ReferenceError.
- Interactive flashcard flip, quiz with per-question answer reveal and final score.

### `UI.tsx`
- `Skeleton`, `CardSkeleton`, `StatSkeleton` — static grey blocks (no shimmer animation yet).
- `ListRow`, `Badge`, `SectionHeader`, `EmptyState` — shared layout components.
- Uses `require('react-native')` inside render functions (anti-pattern but functional).

---

## Services

| Service | Transport | Endpoints |
|---|---|---|
| `api.ts` | Axios + Supabase Bearer | Base: `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` |
| `ai.ts` | Axios | `/api/ai-conversations` (GET, POST, DELETE) |
| `dashboard.ts` | Axios | `/api/stats/me`, `/api/gpa`, `/api/study-plans`, `/api/activity` |
| `documents.ts` | Axios | `/api/pdfs`, `/api/pdfs/:id`, `/api/pdfs/:id/scan` |
| `gpa.ts` | Axios | `/api/gpa` (GET, POST, DELETE) |
| `planner.ts` | Axios | `/api/study-plans` (GET, POST, DELETE) |
| `research.ts` | Edge Fn + Axios | `research-search` (Edge), `/api/research` (GET, DELETE) |
| `leaderboard.ts` | Edge Fn | `get-leaderboard` |
| `chat.ts` | Axios | `/api/chat` (GET, POST) |
| `news.ts` | Axios | `/api/news` |

