| `ai-chat` | `AIScreen`, `ResearchScreen` |
| `parse-pdf` | `LibraryPanel` |
| `generate-study-tools` | `StudyToolsPanel` |
| `get-leaderboard` | `leaderboard.ts` |
| `research-search` | `research.ts` |

