## Key Bugs & Issues Found

> [!CAUTION]
> These will cause runtime crashes or build failures.

| # | File | Bug |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | `ResearchScreen.tsx` | `import * as Clipboard` duplicated (lines 6–7) — TypeScript error |
| 2 | `ResearchScreen.tsx` | `useSafeAreaInsets` used but not imported |
| 3 | `ResearchScreen.tsx` | `expo-clipboard` not in `package.json` |
| 4 | `StudyToolsPanel.tsx` | `pdfContent` referenced instead of `pdfContext` → ReferenceError at runtime |
| 5 | `GPAScreen.tsx` | `chartData` and `Dimensions` used but never declared |
| 6 | `DashboardScreen.tsx` | `insets`, `signOut`, `router` used in JSX but not declared |
| 7 | `LeaderboardScreen.tsx` | `MEDAL` constant not declared |
| 8 | `LibraryPanel.tsx` | `pdf.filePath` / `pdf.file_path` not on `Document` type |
| 9 | `LoginScreen.tsx` | Duplicate `SafeAreaView` import from two packages |

> [!WARNING]
> These are non-crash issues but need addressing.

| # | File | Issue |
|---|---|---|
| 10 | `AIScreen.tsx` | `cleanText` regex double-escape — may not strip `{{...}}` template markers |
| 11 | `ChatScreen.tsx` | No real-time subscription — currently poll-on-mount only |
| 12 | `CoursesScreen.tsx` | No mobile upload capability — users must use web app |
| 13 | `UI.tsx` | Skeleton has no shimmer animation |
| 14 | All screens | Skeleton loading states are inline JSX, not using the `Skeleton` component |
| 15 | `DashboardScreen.tsx` | Loading state renders outside `ScrollView`, ignoring padding from tabs |

