---

## Summary

The app is a well-structured, feature-complete academic companion mobile app. The architecture is clean — one screen per feature, one service per domain, a shared API client, and a consistent dark theme system. The Orbit AI screen is the most sophisticated, supporting streaming AI responses, multi-document PDF context, teach/test session modes, and a full study tools panel.

**The most urgent fixes needed are bugs #1–9** listed above — several screens will crash immediately on render (GPAScreen, DashboardScreen), and StudyToolsPanel will throw a ReferenceError on every generation attempt.
